<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ title }} | DeepSeek 全球產業應用整合</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
  <meta name="keywords" content="DeepSeek, 產業集成, AI 數字轉型, 深度求索, 技術整合, API 方案, 全球化 AI">
  
  <style>
    :root { --primary: #06b6d4; --primary-dark: #0891b2; --bg-dark: #0f172a; --text-main: #334155; --border: #e2e8f0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-main); margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #fff; }
    .container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    
    /* Header */
    .site-header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 25px 0; background: #fff; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000; }
    .header-nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .logo a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--bg-dark); font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .logo div { font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; color: var(--bg-dark); }
    .nav-links { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 30px; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #64748b; font-weight: 500; transition: 0.3s; }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--primary); }

    /* Footer & Friend Links */
    .site-footer { background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 60px 0 30px; margin-top: 80px; }
    .friend-section h4 { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--bg-dark); }
    .friend-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .friend-grid a { text-decoration: none; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; transition: 0.2s; }
    .friend-grid a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    .copy { text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; }
  </style>

  {# 集成 51.la 統計 #}
  <script charset="UTF-8" id="LA_COLLECT" src="//sdk.51.la/js-sdk-pro.min.js"></script>
  <script>LA.init({id:"3K7l95Zodr0uFrIN",ck:"3K7l95Zodr0uFrIN"})</script>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-nav">
      {# H1 智慧管理：首頁使用 H1，內頁降級為 div #}
      {% if page.url == "/" %}
        <h1 class="logo" style="margin:0;"><a href="/">DeepSeek 全球產業應用整合</a></h1>
      {% else %}
        <div class="logo"><a href="/">DeepSeek 全球產業應用整合</a></div>
      {% endif %}
      <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="/" {% if page.url == "/" %}class="active"{% endif %}>智能集成首頁</a></li>
          <li><a href="/posts/" {% if page.url.startsWith('/posts/') %}class="active"{% endif %}>技術檔案中心</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    {{ content | safe }}
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="friend-section">
        <h4>全球 AI 技術生態合作夥伴：</h4>
        <div class="friend-grid">
          <a href="https://deepseek-chat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek 線上智能對話</a>
          <a href="https://hk-deepseek.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek 香港技術社區</a>
          <a href="https://deepseek-in.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek 產業智能集成</a>
          <a href="https://deepseek-1.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek 第一中文教學門戶</a>
          <a href="https://deepseek-my.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DeepSeek 亞太企業智庫中心</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="copy">
        <p>&copy; 2026 DeepSeek 全球產業應用整合中心. 本站受 51.la 精準數據驅動，為企業數字轉型導航.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>